3.1¤Non-contact solution
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If your credit card has a non-contact solution, you may choose to use
this solution when purchasing from businesses offering this solution. You
use the card without inserting it in the terminal. Instead you,
confirm your payment by holding the card in front of
the terminal (at a distance of 0-3 cm) which has activated the non-contact
solution. The non-contact solution is indicated by a symbol on the
terminal.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
There is a limit to the size of the amount you are allowed to pay for each
transaction without having to enter your PIN code, cf. paragraph 2.4.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
3.2¤Dankort card on mobile phone
:SKRSLUT.
.br
I you have a physical Dankort card already, you can have it connected
to your mobile phone. This solution is called Dankort card on mobile
phone. First, you must download an approved wallet for the use of
Dankort card on mobile phone. You will find a list of approved
wallets here:
.br
http://dankort.dk/Pages/Dankort-i-wallets.aspx.
.br
You can register your Dankort card in all approved wallets which have
opened up to Dankort card on mobile phone from &BANKNAVN.. Registration
is done by means of NemID (or similar security). &BANKNAVN. may have
set limits to the number of times you can have the physical Dankort
card connected to your mobile phone.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the process, you must choose the physical card you want to
connect to Dankort card on mobile phone. Furthermore, you will be
asked to choose a personal PIN code to be used if a purchase by
means of Dankort card on mobile phone requires that you enter a
PIN code. Please follow the instructions in your wallet.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
