3¤Using your Visa/Dankort card
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Before you approve a payment or a withdrawal, you must always check
the screen or receipt to make sure that the sum is correct. Once you
have approved a payment, it cannot be revoked. However, see Articles
8 and 9 regarding opportunities for reversing a payment.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In connection with purchases or cash withdrawals, please make sure you get
a receipt. Please also make sure that the amount on the receipt corresponds
to the payment or your purchase, and that the date stated is correct. It is
recommended that you keep the receipt until you have checked that the
correct amount has been withdrawn from your account, see Section 7. It may
occur that no receipt is issued when you make purchases from self-service
terminals.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
