6.2 Modification
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If you wish to change or deregister your mobile phone you can do this using
your NemID on &BANKNAVN.s website or make the change in connection with a
Dankort secured by Nets or Verified by Visa purchase.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
6.3 Special conditions concerning the card and the registered mobile phone
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Your mobile phone is part of the security measures when you purchase goods
from internet shops that subscribe to Dankort secured by Nets or
Verified by Visa. Thus, you
are obliged to secure that others do not have or can get access to your
mobile phone and card at the same time. If you lose the mobile phone on
which you receive temporary PIN-codes, you are obliged to change or
deregister the mobile phone as soon as possible.
If you lose your card you should also block it (see section 10).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
5.¤Power of attorney
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If you want to give power of attorney to another person in order to allow
the person to draw money from your account with aVisa/Dankort card, the
proxy holder must have a personal card and PIN-code. The
person s use of the card is placed under the same legislation
as yourself.
.sp 3mm
If you want to withdraw the power of attorney, you must do so by letter to
&BANKNAVN.. You should call in the card from the proxy holder and return it
to &BANKNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
6. Secure internet payments
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Dankort secured by Nets and Verified by Visa
are extra protection against misuse of card data
when shopping on the internet. Besides the presenting of card data, the
security consist in you entering a temporary code you receive from Nets via
text message in connection with the purchase. The temporary code is only
for use when purchasing in internet shops that subscribe to Dankort secured
by Nets or Verified by Visa.
.sp 3mm
Have you not registered your card to Dankort secured by Nets or Verified
by Visa it is not
possible to use the card in shops that subscribe Dankort secured by Nets
or Verified by Visa.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
6.1 Registration
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Before - or at the latest - in connection with your first purchase in a
shop that subscribes to Dankort secured by Nets or Verified by Visa
you should register your
card to Dankort secured by Nets or Verified by Visa.
.sp 3mm
You use your Dankort card on mobile phone by tapping the specified spot
or the terminal, or by scanning the QR code on the display of the
terminal.
