3.3¤Selv-service machines without PIN code
:SKRSLUT.
.br
In some self-service machines, you can use your Visa/Dankort card
without entering the PIN code or using your signature. In such
cases, you confirm the transaction when your Visa/Dankort card
is read by the machine, or when you press confirm.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
3.4¤Use of credit card number, expiry date and check digits
:SKRSLUT.
.br
When you use your card for purchase e.g. on the internet you are
obliged to enter your card number, expire date and CVV number. If
you use Visa and the shop is subscribing to Verified by Visa, you
will be asked to enter a temporary code you receive via text message
on your mobile phone in connection with the purchase. If you use
Dankort and the shop is subscribing to Dankort Secure you can be
asked to enter the temporary code you receive via text message
from Nets in connection with the purchase (see section 6).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When you use your card to make purchases by mail/telephone order, you
will be required to state your card number, the card expiry date, the
security code and, possibly, your name and address. When making mail
order purchases, you must also sign the order form.
.sp 3mm
Never reveal your PIN code when making purchases via the Internet or in
or in connection with mail/telephone order purchases etc.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You cannot use Dankort card on mobile phone for online purchases or mail
order, and telephone order purchases.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
3.5¤Registration of card data prior to purchase
:SKRSLUT.
.br
It is possible to register all your card data with a specific business or
with a digital wallet provider. Then you need not enter your card data when
confirming future purchases over the Internet with the business/provider in
question. You must follow the directions of the business
or the digital wallet provider.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You will find which digital wallets are approved, with whom you can
register the Dankort part of your Dankort card, here
.br
http://dankort.dk/Pages/Dankort-i-wallets.aspx
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You can also agree with the business in question that your card data are
registered with the business for use in connection with payment of a
subscription. The business in question will withdraw the agreed
subscription payments, thus, you need not confirm each single transaction.
When using your card data in this way you must make sure that any
cancellation of the subscription will take place in accordance with the
terms outlined by the business in question.
.sp 3mm
For all solutions comprised by this Section 3.5 applies that if you replace
your card, you must contact the business or provider of the digital wallet
solution in question to have your new card data registered.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
4¤Keeping your Visa/Dankort card and PIN code safe
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:KURSIV.
Card
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Your card is personal, which means that you are the only person who
may use it. When you receive your card, you must immediately sign the
signature field on the reverse. You must not transfer your card to
other people, or allow others to use it.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Dankort card on mobile phone
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Your Dankort card on mobile phone is personal and must only be used by you.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
PIN code
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Your PIN code is personal, and only you may use it. The PIN code for
your card will be sent to you automatically. When you receive your PIN
code, check whether others may have had access to it.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Learn your PIN code off by heart. You must never store your code
together with your card, write it on the card, or keep the code in or
together with the mobile phone.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You must never give your PIN code to others or otherwise allow
others to become aware of your code. When entering your PIN code, you must
make sure that no one picks up your code.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you suspect that this is the case, contact
&BANKNAVN. immediately and at the same time change the PIN code for
Dankort card on mobile phone.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you cannot remember your code off by heart or wish to write it down
and save it, make sure to keep it in a safe place. If you need to write
your PIN code down use the PIN code reminder you were sent or ask for
one at one of &BANKNAVN.'s branches.
.sp 3mm
